column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: TREBOR EXTRA STRONG GUM SPEARMINT, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 00000050105137
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

INGREDIENTS: Sweeteners (sorbitol, isomalt, maltitol, maltitol syrup, aspartame, sucralose, acesulfame K), gum base, bulking agent (calcium carbonate), flavourings, thickener (gum arabic), humectant (glycerol), colours (E171, lutein, E141, E133), emulsifier (sunflower lecithin), glazing agent (carnauba wax), antioxidant (E321). Excessive consumption may produce laxative effects. Contains a source of phenylalanine.. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 07/25/2016
